casebody.data:
No. 10-11153 (10A1253). Richard Lynn Bible, Petitioner v. Arizona. 564 U.S. 1053, 131 S. Ct. 3092,

180 L. Ed. 2d 913,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5017. June 29, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Kennedy, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Arizona denied.
